<bibRefCitation author="Sturaro MJ &amp; Rodrigues MT &amp; Colli GR &amp; Knowles LL &amp; Avila-Pires TCS" box="[877,1077,485,509]" pageId="13" pageNumber="786" pagination="37 - 65" refId="ref17855" refString="Sturaro MJ, Rodrigues MT, Colli GR, Knowles LL, Avila-Pires TCS (2018) Integrative taxonomy of the lizards Cercosaura ocellata species complex (Reptilia: Gymnophthalmidae). Zoologischer Anzeiger 275: 37 - 65. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. jcz. 2018.04.004" type="journal article" year="2018">Sturaro et al. 2018</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Uetz P &amp; Hosek J" box="[1087,1319,485,509]" pageId="13" pageNumber="786" refId="ref17909" refString="Uetz P, Hosek J (2019) The Reptile Database. http: // www. reptiledatabase. org. Accessed on: 2019 - 5 - 1." type="url" year="2019">Uetz and Hošek 2019</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
